[
  "Mustafa Kucuk is the biggest shareholder of LC Waikiki, a producer and retailer of ready-to-wear fashions and home items.",
  "Kucuk and his partners purchased the business in 1997 and rapidly accelerated growth. Its first international store opened in Romania in 2009.",
  "In 2016, LC Waikiki expanded into home textile products under the brand name LCW Home.",
  "Today, the company has over 1,000 locations in 47 countries; roughly half are outside of Turkey. Its motto: \"Everyone deserves to dress well.\"",
  "Kucuk's partner, Sefik Yilmaz Dizdar, is also a billionaire."
]